---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Jason Ehlinger — Veteran Entrepreneur & Leadership Coach"
  description="Jason Ehlinger is the CEO of Taika Translations, a U.S. Air Force veteran, father of 8, and leadership and personal finance coach. Built a 7-figure business from a card table with no investors."
  keywords="Jason Ehlinger, veteran entrepreneur, leadership coach, CEO Taika Translations, Air Force veteran, personal finance expert, business coach, entrepreneur story, building wealth from nothing, military entrepreneur, faith-based leadership"
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <img
      src="/jason-headshot.jpg"
      alt="Jason Ehlinger"
      style="width:160px; height:160px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; object-position:top; border:4px solid var(--gold); margin-bottom:1.5rem; display:block; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"
    />
    <span class="section-label">My Story</span>
    <h1>I Don't Teach Theory.<br/>I Teach What I Lived.</h1>
    <p>Built from nothing. Broken and rebuilt. Now teaching others the system that changed everything.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">

      <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">From Card Table to 7 Figures</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">My name is Jason Ehlinger. I'm the CEO of <a href="https://www.taikatranslations.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Taika Translations</a>, a veteran-owned multimillion-dollar professional translation and language services company. We built it from a card table in our living room — no investors, no trust fund, no safety net. Just two people figuring it out.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Before that, I served in the U.S. Air Force. The military gave me discipline, structure, and a deep understanding of what it means to operate under pressure. But when I transitioned into entrepreneurship, I quickly discovered that military-style command doesn't translate directly into business leadership.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">I made painful mistakes. I had a team but no real leadership system. I was hustling constantly but getting nowhere fast. I was operating my business instead of leading it. That's when I went deep — into frameworks, systems, faith, and hard lessons.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2.5rem;">What came out of that season was a leadership operating system that changed everything for me and for Taika. And now, I want to give it to you.</p>

      <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:2.5rem 0;"/>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Money Was Always Part of the Mission</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">While building Taika, my wife and I were also on our own financial journey. We figured out how to save $100k on a military salary. We had the hard conversations about money in marriage. We built wealth from zero — methodically, intentionally, without shortcuts.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">That's what the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Vision Tribe Money YouTube channel</a> is about. We share everything — budgeting, wealth building, financial mindset, money in relationships, and creating a life on your own terms. 777+ videos and counting.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Leadership and finance aren't separate topics in my world. They're two sides of the same coin: both require systems, discipline, intentionality, and a clear mission.</p>

      <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin:2.5rem 0;"/>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Faith, Family, and Why It All Matters</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem;">I'm a husband and a father of 8. Leadership starts at home before it starts in the boardroom. My faith is central to everything I do — at Taika, we operate with a Christ-centered commitment to quality and integrity.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2.5rem;">I believe your toughest season can become your greatest blessing. I believe security is an illusion — and that's actually freeing. I believe the reason you work determines everything about how you work. These aren't bumper sticker slogans. They're convictions I've earned.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDENTIALS -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Background</span>
        <h2>By the Numbers</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:900; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">7-Fig</div>
          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Revenue Built</div>
          <div style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Taika Translations, from scratch</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:900; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">8</div>
          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Kids</div>
          <div style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Leadership starts at home</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:900; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">777+</div>
          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Videos</div>
          <div style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Vision Tribe Money on YouTube</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:900; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">USAF</div>
          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Veteran</div>
          <div style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">U.S. Air Force — discipline built in</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div style="font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:900; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">$0</div>
          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Investor Capital</div>
          <div style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Built on grit, systems, and faith</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-dark text-center">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
      <span class="section-label">Let's Connect</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1rem;">Ready to Build Something That Lasts?</h2>
